title: critical infrastructure owners and operators
extract: It draws on all its partners to do so, including other owners and operators of critical infrastructure, state and territory governments, and Australian Government agencies. CIPMA supports the work of the Trusted Information Sharing Network (TISN) for critical infrastructure resilience.Nov 11, 2018
